        "en_title": "The U.S. reiterate, 'contrary to the operation at Rafah'",
        "en_content": "The United States reaffirms\ntheir opposition to a great Israeli operation Rafah. I do.\nstates the spokesman of the US State Department after\nIsraeli Prime Minister Benyamin Netanyahu announced for\nwhich there would already be \"a date\" for the blitz in the last city\nsouthern Gaza bordering Egypt.\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
